Moving Avergae

if MA50 is greater than MA 100 so buy and when MA 50 is smaller than MA 100 then sell.

Hence whenever you are buying ensure, it is a blue candle day and whenever you are selling, ensure it’s a red candle day.
Enter near EOD (End of Day) when price is clearly above yesterday’s high or showing strong bullish bias — not early morning when color can flip.”

history repeat itself so find the trend.hindalco


